{"h8c319f16g2b04g4105ga1bfg11f4f7274211": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "f00f7553-9197-45cd-b177-8e5174671863"], "hd555372eg0817g47ccga33fgd97530340c24": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "d82b7836-86a3-40dd-bc3b-cc1e100a10fc"], "h12cb2175gd97eg4d82g875cgb9f458a5b6ba": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "dc86d7ee-b139-43b2-a139-406797740246"], "hcb2379dfgd16ag46efg9affg32d035a1d493": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "e381402a-bd6f-4dce-a69e-27b620d9a14f"], "h88a6d22fg2723g4bc7g993fg5902d1fd7fc8": ["Volothamp... Geddarm. My mother's... son.", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "d2eb2b8f-491f-4844-88a9-22d824c1b202"], "hf86771beg071ag4d36g940eg6e56adcc9de4": ["What were you doing here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "a8314920-46f8-4c9a-9064-f5af374b0441"], "h9c5ca87bg7391g4b37ga5f2g7a64db0a6fda": ["Investigating... the Absolute. Goblins'...new god.", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "e7247b32-0c03-4ed1-9aa0-5eb70c9a6104"], "h34fab60dg1f70g4b7aga9f9g0a7769a7b15b": ["Who is the Absolute?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "7fdfff58-412c-40a8-b96e-5b03e44eb891"], "h20eb65b7ga56bg4c0cg9c73g2cff05d6fb96": ["Unreal god... unheard of... spread like a plague. ", "2af25a85-5b9a-4794-85d3-0bd4c4d262fa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "f7b8f3ec-ee14-48ae-9584-4be7f3862684"], "hc98af00ag0f30g4680g9d24gb468076314a0": ["Do you have anything of value?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Volo_Dead.html", "5af6e0a0-3ed8-4d2b